---
title: American Chicken, Bacon & Charred Corn Salad with Wholemeal Garlic Croutons & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: You’re not going to believe how simple it is to make this charred corn and chicken salad yourself, from crunchy wholemeal
croutons to herby mayo and tender smokey chicken. Once you’ve got this baby down, dinner time will be a breeze.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66cfd1b75e32858493913433-bef5f833.jpeg
